\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
g(600,35) & =(0.0379147-0.000346514(35))600\\
 & \approx15.47
\end{align*}

\end_inset

is still considerably less than 
\begin_inset Formula $17$
\end_inset

â€”and likely an overestimate.
 
\end_layout

